column5: awesome day on a remote stocked lake!  more than 30 specks landed in a few hours!  gonna test out my new deep fryer tomorrow!
sweet. at one a day, you can head back in on Friday for a refil
Any day on the water is a good day, but that makes me jealous!  S.
Amazing numbers, and looks like a really good average size too.  You live in polkadot heaven!
average size was very good.  very fat, aggressive fish.   numerous doubles and had fish hitting right at the canoe.  gonna take a few "cold certifieds" to come down from such a great day.
A Speck and University of Texas fan!
The Doc was in da house... YO!  Great haul right there.
Only thing better would be nailing stacked beauties
Awesome!!! Have to love specks, and, especially when they reach that size!
Wow, 30 specks in a day is is fantastic. Did you use dynamite? I can smell the deep fryer now. Thanks.
I have yet to catch a speck and you catch 30...geez
who needs dynamite when you've got the doctor spoon and countdown raps!
Awesome day Doc. Countdown Raps are high on my list for Brookies too!
Great haulin there.  30 Specks has to be up there as a monumental day!  RJ
